HEADWORD: Tertial
<hw>Ter"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a. & n.</pos> <ety>[From L.
<ets>tertius</ets> third, the tertial feathers being feathers of the
third row. See <er>Tierce</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Same as
<er>Tertiary</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
